  "body": "When using `go-ethereum` as a library, calling programs need to set the FD limits too themselves, otherwise they run out of descriptors (e.g. running go-ethereum + go-ipfs in a single process on Rinkeby will take about 1 minute for fd's to exhaust and produce bad blocks due to db unavailability).\r\n\r\nMy suggestion is to separate out the fd limit related files into a reusable package, perhaps in `common/fdlimit`.\r\n  ",
